data.description: TIS' THE SEASON! HOLIDAY HOME SPECIAL?! New price point AND seller is including a 1 YEAR HOME WARRANTY!! ARE YOU LOOKING TO START 2024 OFF WITH A BANG? Don't miss out on seeing this LOVELY RESIDENCE! Pristine home located in the CEDARBROOK neighborhood (not far from Chestnut Hill!) Built in 2009, this single family home provides 4 SPACIOUS BEDROOMS, 4 FULL BATHROOMS and 1 HALF BATH?! Upon entering, you'll notice the living room provides ample space to take advantage of. With it's 9 FT CEILINGS and OPEN LAYOUT, no one will ever feel too crowded. The beautiful rich HARDWOOD FLOORS and warm SUNLIT WINDOWS allow for the perfect reading room or place to kick back and relax, after a long day at work. This room is also large enough to utilize as a living/dining room combo. An additional convenience, is the HALF BATHROOM on the main floor. Past the half bath, you'll find a delightful CUSTOM KITCHEN. BEAUTIFULLY designed, the kitchen includes OVERSIZED cabinets, GRANITE countertops with a breakfast island, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES including a gas range, plus so much more. This kitchen is perfect for those who enjoy cooking and bringing their culinary ideas to life! The kitchen opens to a dining/family room area, complete with a built-in GAS FIREPLACE. It's a great space for hosting those Sunday football gatherings! Heading upstairs, there is a PRIMARY EN SUITE. Enjoy the PRIVACY of a tranquil bedroom connecting to DOUBLE WALK-IN HALLWAY CLOSETS. The Jaccuzi tub, tiled shower and DOUBLE VANITY creates the ideal en suite bathroom oasis. Down the hallway you'll find the 2nd bedroom with tons of windows, creating a warm and cozy vibe. Completing the 2nd level, there is a full bathroom and LAUNDRY ROOM. Upstairs on the 3rd level are 2 additional GIANT-SIZED bedrooms and another full bathroom. Downstairs on the lower level you are greeted by a FULLY FINISHED basement. The basement has laminate plank flooring, a BONUS ROOM and final full bathroom. The bonus room is large enough to have a potential bedroom, office, art space, etc. The basement also provides easy access to the mechanical room and an ATTACHED 1-CAR GARAGE. Outback, the property also has a deck and  FANTASTIC PATIO enclosed with 6 FT PRIVACY FENCING. An amazing spot to host large gatherings with family and friends! This home truly is a GEM. With over 3,000 SQFT of living space, IMMACULATE hardwood floors throughout, SPACIOUS bedrooms, MULTIPLE bathrooms and a plethora of other conveniences. QUICK COMMUTE TO CENTER CITY, restaurants, parks and shops. Close proximity to major routes like 76 and LINCOLN DRIVE. If you are looking for a FABULOUS HOME with tons of amenities, this is it?! DON'T DELAY, SCHEDULE YOUR HOME SHOWING TODAY!!!
